text:
Good job, Juri.
The live performance was really great.

Haha,
truthfully, it was really fun!

Everyone in Houkura wore matching outfits, right?
Just that made me happy...

Being united as five people,
our bond naturally strengthened.

From now on, let's work even harder
to make amazing stages.

Let's make everyone
who supports us happy...!

So, please continue to support us,
Producer.
